ated garlic","1 ½ Tbsp dried thyme","1 ½ Tbsp dried oregano","2 tsp ground cayenne pepper","2 tsp ground black pepper","½ tsp ground cumin","½ tsp dark brown muscovado sugar"]},{"title":"Whole Chicken","content":["1 whole uncooked chicken (1.2-1.5 kg)","1000 g water"]}],"id":"r116097","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-fomfohbcrAE\/XZQvuCm5fqI\/AAAAAAAAce8\/7nUoCPCdaqIzqjJWcazIpGuUJr-idLqfQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Kyz3Ev0W2LdciFji.png","title":"Whole Steamed Chicken with Spicy Cajun Rub","publishedAt":"2016-12-26T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"55 g","fat":"24.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"21.7 g","calories":"2214 kJ \/ 529 kcal"},"usefulItems":"airtight jar, serving platter","hintsAndTricks":["The rub on its own makes a great gift idea for friends and family.","Ensure your stuffing is completely cool before using.","To check your chicken is cooked, slice the chicken behind it's leg near to the chest. If the juices run clear, it is cooked.","If you don't want to use a stuffing in your chicken or time is limited, fill the chicken cavity with 2 garlic cloves, sliced, 1 whole lemon, halved and 2 sprigs fresh rosemary in step 6 and proceed as per recipe.<em><br><\/em>"],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 25m","4 portions"]}